{"about_the_game":"<strong>Spin, roll and launch</strong> your way to victory in this fun action puzzle game for all ages, designed to test your reflexes, skillful movement and watchful eye! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515970/extras/001.png?t=1613331861\" /><br><br>Carefully weave your way through <strong>40 stages</strong> of beautifully crafted, colourful stages chocked-full of hazardous <i>spike traps</i>, <i>menacing slimes</i>, <i>laser beams, fire-spouting turrets and angry <strong>Glorbs</strong>!</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515970/extras/001.gif?t=1613331861\" /><br><br><strong>With a barrage of levels</strong> to keep you rolling, a <i>hidden bonus mode</i> to test even the hardiest of enthusiasts, <strong>hidden collectibles</strong> and an <strong>extra pack of stages</strong> that mix up the classic Spin &amp; Roll formula, there's plenty of content to tackle!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515970/extras/002.png?t=1613331861\" /><br><br>There's a whole heap of <strong>hazards and traps</strong> to watch out for when you're spinning your way through the weaving, winding stages of <strong>Spin &amp; Roll</strong>. Some just need dodging, others may <strong>hunt you down</strong>...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515970/extras/003.png?t=1613331861\" /><br><br><strong>Master your progress</strong> on each stage by collecting your winning trophy. Can you beat the level faster? Find all of the <strong>secret tokens</strong>? Get to the goal without losing a ball? Grab the best trophy you can on each stage and you may just unlock an <i>even more challenging</i> take on familiar stages...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515970/extras/004.png?t=1613331861\" /><br><br>The game now includes our first free content update: <strong>Mekanika</strong>! <i>15 levels</i> packed with steampunk-inspired traps, hazards, enemies and visuals!<br><br>Savania is committed to our <strong><i>Content Promise</i></strong> - working to provide you with plenty of completely free DLC to continue supporting this game after launch. We believe in giving back to the players who help to support our games &lt;3","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Rolling!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515970/e8d287ee0d68fbf1cc14787dd9ba511975f5db47.jpg"},{"name":"Voidwalker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515970/72b7079ce532daeeb9ad9c7ee7392e2edc261e2b.jpg"},{"name":"Spare change","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515970/21fcd70076d3e9467d665be7a4dcc86b7d09fdef.jpg"},{"name":"Natural born seeker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515970/f0c60f029ccee652585cd740c66655c4eca13046.jpg"},{"name":"Speed demon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515970/1b1e32deae1000b5b924c085d3430ffb84fa80bf.jpg"},{"name":"Platinum performance","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515970/951b5ec2c20dffc58a317dcf29a2065f1936ad57.jpg"},{"name":"Dedicated","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515970/49d8f7f650d741da81cd5febe2d772d628e80f64.jpg"},{"name":"Class act","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515970/a1a34b439c149d461c5cf3cff2098b0325d903f1.jpg"},{"name":"Ready for more","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515970/3e0995f54c2102838fc3f0a08d61e4ae14c20d49.jpg"},{"name":"Gold standard","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcomm